race.description: Stacks Law Firm Country Boosted Handicap
race.comment: OAKFIELD UTAH (8) started hard in the market on debut when a gritty winner over 1000m at Tamworth. Has plenty of upside and can win again from the wide gate. PURPLE KITTY (5) won well here two-back, then jumped in trip when a battling sixth over 2100m at Tuncurry a week later. Just over a month between runs and expected to run well. CHESTIME (7) returns from a let-up. Failed to handle the five-day backup when raced flat to finish fifth over 1400m at Armidale. Finds an easier race and her best form is over this distance range. Each-way. AYE AYE SKIPPER (6) has failed to fill a placing at his last few runs, the latest when fourth over 1200m at Port Macquarie. Gets chance to feature.
